These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-1::.
House: futuristic, wooden, palace, craftsman, colonial, farmhouse, victorian
1. the colonial house is between the palace house and the wooden house##2
2. the farmhouse house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
3. the victorian house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
4. the farmhouse house is in the middle##1
5. the wooden house is in an odd position##4
6. the palace house is on the left of the colonial house##1
7. the futuristic house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3     |    4    |   5    |    6     |    7     |
| House   | craftsman | victorian | futuristic | farmhouse | palace | colonial | wooden |

