.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: tulip, iris, balloon-flower, bellflower, orchid, rose, begonia
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an even position##4
5. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
6. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2     |   3    |    4     |    5    |  6   |     7      |
| Flower   | orchid | tulip | rose | iris | bellflower | balloon-flower | begonia |

