2. the ranch-style house is on the left of the colonial house##1
3. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
4. the colonial house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
5. the craftsman house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
6. the ranch-style house is on the left of the colonial house##1
7. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
8. the ranch-style house is on the left of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |   2   |      3      |         4          |      5       |     6     |    7    |
| House   | futuristic | craftsman | ranch-style | colonial | townhouse | art-deco | wooden |

