.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-4::.
There are 7 different nationalities: turkish, argentine, spanish, indian, colombian, american, polish
1. the turkish is on the far left or far right##3
2. the american is on the left or right of the indian##3
3. the spanish is in an even position##4
4. the spanish is on the left of the argentine##1
5. the polish is on the right of the turkish##1
6. the spanish is on the right of the colombian##1
7. the argentine is on the left or right of the spanish##3
8. the indian is on the right of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3     |    4     |   5    |     6      |  7   |
| Nationality   | turkish | polish | indian | american | colombian | spanish | argentine |

