.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-5::.
City: venice, berlin, nizza, london, boston, marseilles, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to nizza is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
6. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |    3    |    4     |   5   |   6   |   7    |
| City   | berlin | london | boston | nizza | venice | edinburgh | marseilles |

