2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
7. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2       |     3      |     4      |    5    |     6      |     7      |
| Beverage   | sprite | water | cola | soy-milk | tea | milk | hot-chocolate |

