3. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
5. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
6. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
7. the havana-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|        |  1   |     2     |   3   |     4      |  5   |   6    |   7    |
| Cigar   | bongani | havana | bolivar | dannemann | swisher | baccarat | siglo |

