2. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is in an even position##4
4. the fan of metal is between the fan of r&b and the fan of reggae##2
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
6. the fan of metal is the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3     |    4     |    5    |     6     |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | hip-hop | techno | gospel | r&b | metal | reggae |

