.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-20::.
7 different games are played: scrabble, bridge, backgammon, domino, chess, monopoly, billiard
 1. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 4. the person playing chess is in an odd position##4
 5. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 6. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 8. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
 9. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
10. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |  2   |  3   |  4   |     5      |     6     |  7   |
| Game   | bridge | scrabble | billiard | domino | chess | backgammon | monopoly |

 